General.Name: CTT Systems AB
General.Description: CTT Systems AB (publ) engages in the design, manufacture, and supply of humidity control products for aircraft worldwide. The company offers humidifiers and dehumidifiers for passenger cabins, flight decks, crew rest compartments, and VIP/business jets under Humidifier Onboard name; active moisture control systems for humidity control; and anti-condensation systems that reduces airlines' climate and environmental impact. It serves commercial airliners and private jets. CTT Systems AB (publ) was incorporated in 1991 and is based in Nyköping, Sweden.
